; Coverage for amount.cc (trailing period re-read):
; A trailing period with no following digits indicates zero decimal
; places (hledger compatibility). "$100." is treated as $100 with
; zero precision. Combined with a normal amount, the higher precision
; is used for display.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $200.50
    Assets:Cash

test bal
            $-300.50  Assets:Cash
             $300.50  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
